\b \cf0 \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Narration: 
\b0 The reference list entry requires a lot more information. The simplest and most straightforward one is for an ordinary book. In the reference listing you will give the author's name, this time with an initial, and the year of publication. The name of the books is 
\b italicised
\b0  and is in lowercase except for the first letter. Following that, you need the city of publication and, after the colon, the name of the publisher.\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \cell \row

